title: New n8n AI Course
description: A comprehensive, step-by-step course to help students understand the basics of n8n AI and apply it to solve real-world problems.
learningObjectives: Understand the basics of n8n AI
Develop practical skills to work with n8n AI
Apply n8n AI concepts to design solutions for real-world problems
Understand the ethical considerations of using n8n AI

finalProjectDetails.overview: For the final project, students will design and implement an n8n AI solution for a problem of their choice.
finalProjectDetails.submissionInstructions: Submit your final project via the online learning platform by the end of Week 6
